:**  \n1. Implement automated breach detection and notification via **Informatica Cloud Application Integration (CAI)**.  \n\n---\n\n### 5. Data Retention & Erasure (50% Compliance)\n**Risk Level:** High  \n**Implications:** Untimely deletions violate storage limitation principles.  \n\n**Action Items:**  \n1. Automate erasure workflows with **Informatica Cloud Data Integration (CDI)**.  \n2. Trigger 48-hour deletion notices using **CAI**.  \n\n---\n\n### 6. Data Accuracy (25% Compliance)\n**Risk Level:** Critical  \n**Implications:** Inaccurate data processing voids legal basis.  \n\n**Action Items:**  \n1. Standardize data with **Informatica Cloud Data Quality (CDQ)**.  \n2. Enhance audit logs via **Informatica IICS** for traceability.  \n\n---\n\n### 7. Children’s Data (33.3% Compliance)\n**Risk Level:** High  \n**Action Items:**  \n1. Implement parental consent verification and label child data using **Informatica CDGC**.  \n\n---\n\n### 8. Third-Party Processing (0% Compliance)\n**Risk Level:** Critical  \n**Action Items:**  \n1. Formalize vendor contracts and monitor flows with **Informatica CDPM**.  \n\n---\n\n### 9. Cross-Border Transfers (66.7% Compliance)\n**Risk Level:** Medium  \n**Action Items:**  \n1. Enforce location-based policies via **Informatica CDAM**.  \n\n---\n\n### 10. Documentation (10% Compliance)\n**Risk Level:** Critical  \n**Action Items:**  \n1. Automate documentation with **Informatica Enterprise Data Catalog**.  \n2. Appoint a Data Protection Officer (DPO).  \n\n---\n\n## Strategic Recommendations\n1. **Prioritize High-Risk Areas:** Focus on Third-Party Processing, Documentation, and Breach Notification.  \n2. **Leverage Automation:** Deploy **Informatica solutions** for erasure, logging, and rights management.  \n3. **Training:** Conduct DPDP workshops using **CLAIRE GPT** for policy guidance.  \n\n---\n\n**Partner with Informatica experts to close gaps efficiently.**  \nContact **info@datainfa.com** for DPDP implementation support.  